1.  Install plastex

2.  Copy the "reference.tex" and "definitions.tex" files into this directory.

3.  Run "./plastex.manual pyxplot.gp_help.tex"

4.  Fix any patches that have not applied by applying them manually.
 
5.  Copy the gp_help.xml file to .../pyxplot8/src/ppl_help.xml

6.  Check that ppl help still works

7.  Check it in!

8.  Run diff -u gp_help.xml{.orig,} > gp_help.xml.diff to re-generate the diff with your patches from step 4.
